<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .appointment-card,
        .offering-card,
        .testimonial-card {
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .appointment-card:hover,
        .offering-card:hover,
        .testimonial-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .unavailable {
            opacity: 0.6;
            background-color: #f8d7da;
        }

        .unavailable-text {
            color: red;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .testimonial-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .testimonial-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Clinic Name</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Our Expert Doctors</h2>
        <p>Our clinic is renowned for providing top-notch medical expertise in dermatology and cosmetic treatments.</p>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Clinic Name. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
